channel.title: Is there any source available for download, which doesn't need a custom client?
channel.description:
I'm wondering if there is any source available for download, which doesn't need a custom client to access.
Where could I download this?

item.title: Is there any source available for download, which doesn't need a custom client?
item.dc:creator: @Syrillia Syrillia
item.description:
@Syrillia wrote:

You could try Hybridscape. It’s what Moparscape 3.2 uses. It’s a little bit to set up, but it wouldn’t take long. However there is some work to be done to get it ship-shape.

http://cache.hybridscape.com/MoparScapeSources.jar

Edit: That file includes server and client sources for 317 & 508.
